{"tid":1070242,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"東京奧運公布火炬設計　石原聰美任火炬傳遞大使!!","createTime":"2019-03-20T13:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T19:19:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":58,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8f6b1e661374b29e7743fba882a3a609916dfe","tid":1070242,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"立場報道2019/3/20 &mdash; 20:45<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JNtNvLT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJNtNvLT.png&h=4d297c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本藝人石原聰美、柔道運動員野村忠宏<br />\n東京奧運會組委會今日揭曉 2020年東京奧運會火炬樣式設計，公布奧運火炬在日本國內傳遞計劃。日本演員石原聰美、搞笑藝人組合SandwichMan、運動員野村忠宏、殘奧會選手田口亞希，將會成為火炬傳遞大使。<br />\n<br />\n東京奧運火炬造型的靈感源自櫻花，顏色為「櫻花金」，火炬頂部設計成花瓣狀，奧運火種將從五個「花瓣」及中央「花蕊」部分點燃。火炬整體長度為71厘米，總重量約1.2公斤。火炬主要材質為鋁材。在火炬所用的鋁材中，有三成回收自2011年日本大地震災后的臨時板房。<br />\n<br />\n奧組委指出，參考了知名度和人氣調查後，認為石原聰美等符合火炬大使的形象，最終確定上述人選。消息公布後，石原聰美發布視頻表示：「聽到這樣的消息我在吃驚的同時，感受到了我身上肩負的責任感。我將去拜會火炬手和全國各地的人，並將這些傳達給大家。」<br />\n<br />\n福島縣開始火炬傳遞<br />\n<br />\n火炬在日本的傳遞初段，正值日本櫻花季節，奧運火炬將於2020年3月20日抵達日本，首先將在關東大地震受災地宮城縣、岩手縣及福島縣三縣展示，於3月26日在距離福島縣第一核電站20公里的體育場地 J-village ，正式開始火炬傳遞，歷時121天巡迴47個都道府縣，至明年在7月24日的開幕式上點燃東京新國立競技場的火炬台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/東京奧運公布火炬設計-石原聰美等任火炬傳遞大使/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E7%81%AB%E7%82%AC%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88-%E7%9F%B3%E5%8E%9F%E8%81%B0%E7%BE%8E%E7%AD%89%E4%BB%BB%E7%81%AB%E7%82%AC%E5%82%B3%E9%81%9E%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%2F&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOVwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=3c251a63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E7%81%AB%E7%82%AC%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88-%E7%9F%B3%E5%8E%9F%E8%81%B0%E7%BE%8E%E7%AD%89%E4%BB%BB%E7%81%AB%E7%82%AC%E5%82%B3%E9%81%9E%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%2F&h=fa02d16d\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/東京奧運公布火炬設計-石原聰美等任火炬傳遞大使/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6902f0c2d50d09545c7dc03cdacb0bf92dd945","tid":1070242,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"咁少人傳？"},{"pid":"ddd2fbbf5046e2a91ee86885ab4e9bfa2f0cb47a","tid":1070242,"uid":128298,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"憑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8ffa08ae159175756c55e0a8ba14780d749d32","tid":1070242,"uid":159870,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"今次唔知又抄邊個<br />\n一陣又臨時換<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80faddde54ddc4497e0a008c176eb0614f4ac605","tid":1070242,"uid":213300,"like":5,"dislike":34,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n係到結衣BB啦<br />\n石原憑乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc94f71aa1f9cb3ef5670a88a591316a731df5ee","tid":1070242,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:35:43.000Z","msg":"佢其實有冇整容？"},{"pid":"7319c77bc6024c47ef6d4d94a24f233b4049b495","tid":1070242,"uid":172365,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"dc94f71aa1f9cb3ef5670a88a591316a731df5ee","tid":1070242,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:35:43.000Z","msg":"佢其實有冇整容？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:37:39.000Z","msg":"點會冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1827ba8d7c9aa8ec277e166c6bd5564993e8b386","tid":1070242,"uid":49197,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"聰美太男人味重<br />\n石原里美好聽好多"},{"pid":"6053f6fb79d712d137a521a47d7ae9ac3cb861fc","tid":1070242,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"諗起佢踩單車炒車（劇入面）"},{"pid":"15b48320ab388bad1980ea06ce7e75dcd44d01ae","tid":1070242,"uid":206137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:50:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">東京奧運火炬造型的靈感源自櫻花，顏色為「櫻花金」，火炬頂部設計成花瓣狀，奧運火種將從五個「花瓣」及中央「花蕊」部分點燃。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n未襟入去睇圖個陣我諗起白事啲蓮花點燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />花瓣同花蕊六點火"},{"pid":"4371509a4089171fa72723f96fa9ab6ec89e918d","tid":1070242,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ho ball"},{"pid":"6bfdd4f6a6bd0f0a8bbe502d3d69507a2323ee78","tid":1070242,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:02:51.000Z","msg":"諗起香港果次 一堆建制撚頭 有得跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港火炬手大部份為香港市民，名單有120人，在當日前受到保密處理。當時盛傳政界人士曾蔭權、唐英年及曾憲梓也入圍當火炬手，但在公眾的壓力下，曾蔭權及唐英年均願意讓出火炬手的位置予運動員。<br />\n<br />\n名單於4月29日官方公布。知名火炬手包括李麗珊、黃金寶、王晨、葉姵延、李靜、高禮澤、蔡曉慧、鄭禮騫、陳潤韜、趙頌熙、李剛、曾憲梓、汪明荃、陳志雲、李澤鉅、李家傑、何超瓊、郭炳江、朱經武、吳清輝、葉詠詩、吳小莉、范徐麗泰、鍾建民、崔康常、陳祖澤、張學友、劉德華、古巨基、陳奕迅、陳慧琳、方力申、陳易希劉夢熊等共120位。[1][2][3]<br />\n<br />\n這120名火炬手當中，其中由火炬手遴選委員會提名84名，贊助商提名（可口可樂、三星、☭聯想☭）24名，北京奧組委提名12名。惟官方未有公布個別火炬手的提名是由以上哪個機構推舉。 <br />\n<br />\n🇨🇳中國香港🇨🇳體育協會暨奧林匹克委員會於2008年4月29日宣布火炬手名單，其中包括行政會議召集人梁振英、人大前常委曾憲梓、多名商界人士及若干🇨🇳親中🇨🇳政黨區議員。雖然港協暨奧委會會長霍震霆稱名單是「社會的縮影」，並表示希望社會接受，但不少學者及政界人士仍批評火炬手名單是向商界及🇨🇳親中🇨🇳人士利益輸送、「政治分贓」。批評者還認爲，很多本港傑出運動員，如車菊紅、洪松蔭、張偉良、胡國雄與李健和均告落選，反而許多在香港不知名的人物成功獲選，如多名🇨🇳親中🇨🇳區議員以及由北京奧組委提名的2007年中華小姐、僅來過香港兩次的曾光。香港中文大學政治及行政學系高級導師蔡子強批評，此舉有如國慶活動，令火炬傳遞成為「🇨🇳親中🇨🇳陣營的分餅仔遊戲」[4]。傳媒人梁文道批評火炬手名單「令人憤怒齒冷」「滿布🇨🇳親中🇨🇳權貴」「酬庸氣味濃得中人慾嘔」、提名火炬手過程黑箱作業，他認爲無論外國還是中國大陸，火炬手名單都不乏平民，而香港「天水圍窮苦街坊、SARS疫潮的康復者，以及殉職公務員的家屬」、多名本地傑出運動員紛紛落選，港府在處理此問題上甚至不如🇨🇳內地🇨🇳城市。[5]身兼職工盟主席的立法會議員李卓人更批評火炬手遴選制度為「政治分贓」[6]。"},{"pid":"bac0b9a59243ce90e621485e91cd1446c9565b77","tid":1070242,"uid":2033,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"石原里美&gt;新垣結衣"},{"pid":"9440f70ceb3bd63c09f943ea878a07240c0ff65a","tid":1070242,"uid":219529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"唔係悟空同馬里奧咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b82aa00c94a5389e4657190376c32a004c331f9","tid":1070242,"uid":149494,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"石原真係靚過結衣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbef12340ef6e74a58371ce7eedd5f8f9222e1a","tid":1070242,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f8ffa08ae159175756c55e0a8ba14780d749d32","tid":1070242,"uid":159870,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"今次唔知又抄邊個<br />\n一陣又臨時換<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"當日本係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1e380b0cfbcad39eec96c50c348925cde1e73b","tid":1070242,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80faddde54ddc4497e0a008c176eb0614f4ac605","tid":1070242,"uid":213300,"like":5,"dislike":34,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n係到結衣BB啦<br />\n石原憑乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=